source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_00<tab>Narujj Boh wishes to entrust you with a tiresome─but necessary─task.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_00<tab>Narujj Boh a sûrement une nouvelle tâche à vous confier.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_01<tab>Though the Brotherhood of Ash strives to destroy the fiery talismans of its foe whenever they appear, it lacks the numbers to match the zealous pace of the Flamefangs. Take the sacks of ash given to you by Narujj Boh, and smother all the beacons you find within the Zanr'ak encampment. Be prepared to defend yourself against any retaliation your efforts incur.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_01<tab>Narujj Boh vous a demandé d'éteindre les flammes sacrées du camp de Zanr'ak qui servent à intensifier la protection d'Ifrit. Vous devrez éteindre les quatre <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E917B0302 /var> au moyen <var 33 ((EventItem)) 09F61E89260302 /var>.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_02<tab>You have extinguished all the Amalj'aa beacons within the encampment. Return to the Ring of Ash and report to Narujj Boh.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez utilisé les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89260302 /var> pour éteindre les flammes des <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E917B0302 /var>. Retournez faire votre rapport à Narujj Boh.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_03<tab>You return to the Ring of Ash, tested but triumphant. Narujj Boh is well pleased by your deeds, but warns that the Flamefangs will respond with ever greater acts of foolish fanaticism. He vows, however, the Brotherhood of Ash will never surrender in its efforts to restore the ancient and honorable ways of the Amalj'aa.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_SEQ_03<tab>Narujj Boh est satisfait de votre réussite, et plus décidé que jamais à contrecarrer les plans de ses ennemis. Poursuivez votre col<var 16 /var>la<var 16 /var>bo<var 16 /var>ra<var 16 /var>tion avec la Ligue dès que l'occasion se présentera.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E3E802E804 ((Use smothering ash to extinguish Amalj'aa beacons.)) ((Use smothering ash to extinguish the last beacon, and defeat any Flamefangs that appear.)) /var>
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E3E802E804 ((Utiliser <var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E89260202 /var> sur les 4 <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E917B0302 /var> de Zanr'ak)) ((Utiliser <var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E89260202 /var> sur le 4e <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E917B0202 /var> et vaincre le Croc de Feu)) /var>
TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_TODO_01<tab>Faire un rapport à Narujj Boh

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_000<tab>Attend me, honored ally. Our Zahar'ak foes yet shelter the potent flames of Ifrit, and fuel their endless rites with his unholy fire.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_000<tab>Salutations, puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> guerri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>. Depuis longtemps, la flamme née du souffle du Dieu des flammes infernales, nos ennemis utilisent pour leurs cérémonies.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_001<tab>Once more do they erect blazing beacons within their camp, in a bid to forever dwell under the heat of their deity's savage blessing. How many times must we topple these foul talismans?
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_001<tab>Pour accroître la protection du Dieu, ce feu, nos ennemis ont placé sur <var 33 ((EObj)) 02F61E917B0202 /var>. La flamme, nous avons éteint par le passé à maintes reprises.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_002<tab>We have not the numbers to prevent their constant reappearance. Thus, again, I must turn to you for aid.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_002<tab>Mais la fréquence de ces cérémonies, ils augmentent. Besoin de ton appui pour les interrompre, nous avons.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_003<tab>I would have you slip inside the boundaries of the encampment with this smothering ash, and extinguish all the beacons you can find.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_003<tab>Trouver quatre <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E917B0302 /var> dans le camp de Zanr'ak, tu devras. Jeter dessus le contenu d'<var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E89260202 /var>, il te faudra pour en étouffer la flamme.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_004<tab>The Flamefangs have, however, grown wary of our incursions, and posted veteran sentinels to guard against our attacks. Expect your efforts to be met with furious retaliation.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_004<tab>De puissants facteurs de motivation, ces flambeaux sont. Un coup au moral, les détruire leur porterait. Une réaction violente, ils auront bien sûr. À te battre, tu dois être prêt<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_010<tab>As of this moment, our scouts report four beacons within the Zanr'ak encampment. Take with you the sacks of smothering ash, and put out these flames spawned of Ifrit's searing breath!
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_010<tab>Les quatre <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E917B0302 /var> de Zanr'ak, tu dois trouver<var 1D /var>! Les éteindre, tu devras au moyen de <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E89260202 /var>.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_020<tab>The unholy flames of Ifrit no longer wink at us in the darkness. You have once more deprived our foe of a potent source of strength.
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_020<tab>La flamme de nos ennemis, tu as pu éteindre<var 1D /var>! De gratitude envers toi, mon cœur est rempli.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_021<tab>I wish only that your victory were more permanent─the Flamefangs will respond, doubtless with their characteristic zealotry. But the Brotherhood of Ash cannot─<var 1A 02 /var>will not<var 1A 01 /var>─be swayed from its path!
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_NARUJIBOH_000_021<tab>Intensifier leurs activités, les Crocs de Feu vont pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment. Mais nos efforts, nous ne relâcherons pas. Plus forte, notre ténacité sera. Sans faille, notre volonté sera.
TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_POP_MESSAGE_000_000<tab>Action impossible. Vous devez d'abord abattre tous les ennemis.

source: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_POP_BALLOON<tab>You violate the sacred flame, unbeliever!
target: TEXT_BANAMA204_01235_POP_BALLOON<tab>Éteindre ce feu, nous ne vous laisserons pas<var 1D /var>!
